reviews.review_text: www.sugarmegs.org Have been a fan of GD for many years now. Does anyone know why that other excellent site (sugarmegs) seems to be saturating their site with GD gigs? Especially strange when recordings here are split into individual tracks.
Thank you Have a nice day 😊

Seastones This was an epic night. I was already high when during the set break behind me I hear, whoosh clink, whoosh clink. I turn around and three guys are doing whippets. I never did nitrous oxide before but just as I took a hit Ned and Phil began playing Seastones…
